Note:
Runa Standard Library: AI Knowledge Taxonomy Module Stub
Provides comprehensive taxonomic classification and hierarchical reasoning capabilities
Enables automatic classification, multi-faceted taxonomies, and taxonomic evolution
:End Note

Type TaxonomySystem is Dictionary with:
    system_id as String
    taxonomy_type as String
    classification_scheme as ClassificationScheme
    taxonomy_structure as TaxonomyStructure
    classification_engine as ClassificationEngine
    hierarchy_manager as HierarchyManager
    validation_framework as ValidationFramework
    evolution_tracker as EvolutionTracker
    mapping_system as MappingSystem
    system_configuration as SystemConfiguration

Type ClassificationScheme is Dictionary with:
    scheme_id as String
    scheme_name as String
    scheme_type as String
    classification_levels as List[ClassificationLevel]
    classification_criteria as List[ClassificationCriterion]
    notation_system as NotationSystem
    scope_definition as ScopeDefinition
    authority_control as AuthorityControl
    scheme_maintenance as SchemeMaintenance

Type TaxonomyStructure is Dictionary with:
    structure_id as String
    root_nodes as List[TaxonomyNode]
    hierarchy_depth as Integer
    branching_factor as BranchingFactor
    node_relationships as List[NodeRelationship]
    cross_references as List[CrossReference]
    structural_constraints as List[StructuralConstraint]
    structure_statistics as StructureStatistics

Type TaxonomyNode is Dictionary with:
    node_id as String
    node_label as String
    node_type as String
    node_level as Integer
    parent_nodes as List[TaxonomyNode]
    child_nodes as List[TaxonomyNode]
    sibling_nodes as List[TaxonomyNode]
    node_properties as Dictionary
    classification_code as String
    scope_notes as List[ScopeNote]
    authority_information as AuthorityInformation

Type ClassificationEngine is Dictionary with:
    engine_id as String
    classification_algorithms as List[ClassificationAlgorithm]
    feature_extractors as List[FeatureExtractor]
    similarity_measures as List[SimilarityMeasure]
    decision_strategies as List[DecisionStrategy]
    confidence_assessment as ConfidenceAssessment
    automatic_classification as AutomaticClassification
    manual_classification as ManualClassification

Type ClassificationResult is Dictionary with:
    result_id as String
    classified_item as ClassifiedItem
    assigned_categories as List[AssignedCategory]
    classification_confidence as Float
    classification_reasoning as ClassificationReasoning
    alternative_classifications as List[AlternativeClassification]
    classification_metadata as ClassificationMetadata
    quality_assessment as QualityAssessment

Type HierarchyManager is Dictionary with:
    manager_id as String
    hierarchy_operations as List[HierarchyOperation]
    node_management as NodeManagement
    relationship_management as RelationshipManagement
    hierarchy_validation as HierarchyValidation
    hierarchy_optimization as HierarchyOptimization

Type ValidationFramework is Dictionary with:
    framework_id as String
    validation_rules as List[ValidationRule]
    validation_engine as ValidationEngine
    quality_metrics as List[QualityMetric]
    validation_reports as List[ValidationReport]
    compliance_checking as ComplianceChecking

Type EvolutionTracker is Dictionary with:
    tracker_id as String
    evolution_history as List[EvolutionEvent]
    change_management as ChangeManagement
    version_control as VersionControl
    impact_analysis as ImpactAnalysis
    rollback_capabilities as RollbackCapabilities

Type MappingSystem is Dictionary with:
    system_id as String
    mapping_algorithms as List[MappingAlgorithm]
    mapping_rules as List[MappingRule]
    mapping_validation as MappingValidation
    mapping_optimization as MappingOptimization
    cross_reference_management as CrossReferenceManagement

Type SystemConfiguration is Dictionary with:
    config_id as String
    system_parameters as Dictionary
    performance_settings as PerformanceSettings
    security_settings as SecuritySettings
    integration_settings as IntegrationSettings
    monitoring_settings as MonitoringSettings

Process called "create_taxonomy_system" that takes config as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "construct_taxonomy" that takes taxonomy_system as Dictionary and construction_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "classify_item" that takes taxonomy_system as Dictionary and classification_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "perform_automatic_classification" that takes feature_data as Dictionary and classification_engine as Dictionary and taxonomy_system as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "navigate_taxonomy" that takes taxonomy_system as Dictionary and navigation_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "validate_taxonomy_structure" that takes taxonomy_system as Dictionary and validation_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "evolve_taxonomy" that takes taxonomy_system as Dictionary and evolution_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "map_taxonomies" that takes taxonomy_system as Dictionary and mapping_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "search_taxonomy" that takes taxonomy_system as Dictionary and search_context as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "create_taxonomy_monitoring_system" that takes configuration as Dictionary returns Dictionary
Process called "execute_taxonomy_analysis" that takes system as Dictionary and query as Dictionary returns Dictionary 